section.about:
Hi, I‘m Eris, I am married and have two children. Aside of hosting the guests, we run a travel agency and tour operator here in Tirana.
Traveling often we want to offer our guests what we would like to have when we stay in other places: first courtesy and then cleanliness.

htmlDescription.htmlText:
The newest charming, contemporary house in the heart of Tirana city. Just couple blocks away from amazing restaurants, Skanderbeg square, cafes, bars, see sights, and so much more. One of the best pastry shops- Le Bon is on the first floor of the building. Perfect for weekend getaway, business trip, staycation, work-from-home alternative (100Mbps)or cozy home base while
exploring everything Mozart has to offer. In all its spaces there are large windows with thermyc glasses.The airport is 25 min.

reviews.comments: a really nice room, good bed and nice view
A very nice place. Very clean and at a very nice location.
Well located in Tirāna city Center
Appartamento moderno situato a 5 minuti dalla piazza principale numerosi ristoranti e locali nei dintorni , rapporto qualità prezzo ottimo , host super disponibile. Consigliatissimo

localizedReview.comments: Modern apartment located 5 minutes from the main square, numerous restaurants and clubs nearby, great value for money, super helpful host. Highly recommended

reviews.comments: A brilliant airbnb with a spectacular view of Tirana and the surrounding scenery. Very good host and super communicative with clear check in. Thank you!
Come descritto

Eris was a great host! The place was great, we felt safe as two girls who have never been to tirana!
You had a gorgeous cafe downstairs named Le bon with great pastries, cakes etc

The apartment was sparkling clean especially the sheets!!. Eris was very helpful with instructions on how to get into the apartment and local shops to get a few stuff we needed. The WIFI was super fast and we enjoyed our stay in Tirana 😊
Really nice place, Eris was helpful

Tirana me ha encantado y tener un lugar donde descansar y disfrutar  la ciudad es muy importante. Hemos disfrutado mucho de Mozzart  Luxury Appartments. Es como sale en las fotos del anuncio. Lo recomiendo 100%.

localizedReview.comments: Tirana loved it and having a place to rest and enjoy  the city is very important. We enjoyed Mozzart  Luxury Appartments a lot. It's how it looks in the listing photos. I recommend it 100%.

reviews.comments: Excellent modern and stylish balcony apartment, right in a cool neighbourhood section of central Tirana, with a stunning Mountain view, very good value.
Everything was perfect and very clean
We enjoyed this apt :)
Modern and clean apartment close to center. Outside area was very nice with my morning coffee

The apartment looks like the pictures, is very clean and the balcony is nice. however, we had booked it mainly because the service that you can leave your luggage on late departure is offered. Unfortunately, the service was not offered. We could only leave our luggage for 3 hours after checkout but our flight was late in the evening. Because of the luggage we had to cancel our plans for the day and could not enjoy our last day in Tirana, which was very annoying.

Really centrally situated and enjoyed walking from here.
Also we foolishly locked ourselves out the first day, and she responded immediately and kindly came to put the key back in the lock box for us.

Eris was a very nice host and responded whenever I needed it. Even when there was trouble in the appartment complex, Eris was making sure it would be fixed and kept me posted during the proces.
The appartment was very modern and clean and I really liked staying there. The best thing about the appartment, in my opinion, is the balcony with the view of Mt. Dajti!
Thankyou Eris!
Super schöne Unterkunft , mitten in der Stadt . Alles zu Fuß zu erreichen . Eris ist ein super freundlicher Gastgeber , sehr hilfsbereit bei allen Fragen .

localizedReview.comments: Super nice place , right in the middle of the city . Everything within walking distance. Eris is a super friendly host , very helpful with any questions .

reviews.comments: The host was really responsive and helpful, replying super quickly to all / any queries we had. The location was great, super easy to get to the central square, the parks and also great transportation links for outside of Tirana. Overall this is a great stay for a good price! Thank you!
Sehr sauberes und komfortables AirBnb, direkt in der Stadtmitte. Alles super zu erreichen. Alles was besprochen wurde, wurde eingehalten und die Kommunikation war sehr schnell und unkompliziert.

localizedReview.comments: Very clean and comfortable AirBnb, right in the city center. Everything super to achieve. Everything that was discussed was complied with and the communication was very quick and easy.

reviews.comments:

Restaurante, mercado , bares e o centro
Tudo muito organizado e limpo

Very beautiful the apartment, close to everything
Restaurant, Market , Bars & Downtown

reviews.comments: My stay at Eris' Airbnb was lovely. Everything is new in the apartment, it feels fresh and clean. The views are fantastic, too. The location is perfect, very central to everything one might need. Eris' communication was fast and friendly. My stay was great, I highly recommend staying at Eris' apartment while visiting Tirana!
